high_descs: Turn to the left to face the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife from inside the sink to the right.
Open the cabinet directly below the sink to the right and place the knife inside of the green bowl.
Pick up the green bowl with the knife in it and close the cabinet door.
Move slightly to the left to face the sink on the left.
Place the green bowl in the sink on the left.
anns.task_desc: Move the green bowl with the knife inside of it to the left sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the wash basin.
Pick up the butter knife from inside the wash basin.
Open the cabinet below the wash basin.
Pick up the green ice cream bowl from the cabinet.
Place the butter knife in the bowl.
Turn around and walk two step and then turn right and turn right again towards the small sink and place the ice cream bowl in the left side small sink.
anns.task_desc: Get the butter knife in an ice cream bowl and put in small sink.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and put the knife in the green cup.
Pick up the green cup with knife in the cabinet.
Bring the green cup with knife to the left sink.
Put the cup with knife in the sink on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with knife in the left sink.
